OL,6,FThe document said problems arise when
OL,7,Fhospitals have lower patient numbers.
OL,9,FIt said: "To address this, we need to
OL,10,Fdevelop regional centres of excellence
OL,11,For surgical hubs for some inpatient
OL,12,Fservices, especially where the
OL,13,Fcatchment area of our existing
OL,14,Fhospitals is too small to provide this.
OL,16,F"Regional centres of excellence,
OL,17,Frather than small local services in
OL,18,Fevery area, deliver better outcomes
OL,19,Ffor both patients and clinicians.
